{"id":680610501,"lang":"cpp","time":"3 days, 19 hours","timestamp":1649993582,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"173 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/680610501/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Array Nesting","memory":"91.3 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int arrayNesting(vector<int>& nums) {\n        int n = nums.size();\n        int ans = 0;\n        for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {\n            int j = i;\n            int s = 0;\n            while(nums[j] >= 0) {\n                int tmp = nums[j];\n                nums[j] = -1;\n                j = tmp;\n                ++s;\n            }\n            ans = max(ans, s);\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"array-nesting"}
